---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Git Note" description="Git講座プロジェクト Git Note の紹介">
  <div class="redirect-container">
    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    <div class="card" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <div class="icon-wrap">
        <img src="/img/notes/gitnote/gitnote-icon-new.svg" alt="Git Note" />
      </div>
      <h1 class="rainbow-text">Git Note</h1>
      <p>
        Git を使った共同開発チュートリアル。<br />
        ハチの巣をみんなで作りながら、OSSの世界へ飛び込もう。
      </p>
      <a href="https://gitnote.rubydog.jp" class="go-btn" data-magnetic>
        gitnote.rubydog.jp へ移動
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .redirect-container {
    min-height: 65vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .orb-1 { width: 350px; height: 350px; background: var(--green); top: 10%; left: 10%; }
  .orb-2 { width: 250px; height: 250px; background: var(--blue); bottom: 10%; right: 15%; }

  .card {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 480px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .icon-wrap {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    background: var(--light-green);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .icon-wrap img { width: 50px; height: 50px; object-fit: contain; }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .go-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--green);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(5,172,71,0.2);
  }
  .go-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(5,172,71,0.3);
  }
</style>
